text: Kaya Özcan (born 1945) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco- Roman 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Doğubeyazıt
